aa(lp96
VFor example, Ayr Muir in Boston knew he wanted to open a restaurant.
p97
aVBut where should it be?
p98
aVWhat should the menu be?
p99
aVHe launched a service,
p100
aVin this case a food truck,
p101
aVand he changed the location each day.
p102
